---
// EDGE — The EmotionOS for Human Connection
// src/pages/index.astro
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EDGE — The EmotionOS for Human Connection</title>
  <meta name="description" content="We decode physiological signals into real-time guidance for synchronized intimacy. Bridging the Pleasure Gap." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,600&family=Space+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --black:    #080706;
      --off-white: #F0EDE6;
      --warm-mid: #8C8279;
      --warm-faint: #1A1714;
      --rose:     #D4735A;
      --rose-dim: #7A3C2A;
      --rose-glow: rgba(212, 115, 90, 0.18);
      --gold:     #C4A96A;
      --border:   rgba(240, 237, 230, 0.08);
      --border-warm: rgba(240, 237, 230, 0.14);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--black);
      color: var(--off-white);
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      cursor: default;
    }

    /* ─── GRAIN OVERLAY ─── */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9999;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    /* ─── TYPOGRAPHY ─── */
    .display {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 0.92;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .display-italic {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    .mono-label {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
    }

    /* ─── HEADER ─── */
    header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 28px 48px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: border-color 0.4s, background 0.4s;
    }
    header.scrolled {
      border-color: var(--border);
      background: rgba(8, 7, 6, 0.88);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    }
    .logo {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--off-white);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .logo span { color: var(--rose); }

    nav { display: flex; gap: 40px; }
    nav a {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    nav a:hover { color: var(--off-white); }

    .btn-outline {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--off-white);
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
      padding: 10px 24px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--rose); color: var(--rose); }

    /* ─── HERO ─── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100svh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      padding: 0 48px 80px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-bg-text {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -56%);
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: clamp(120px, 22vw, 300px);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-style: italic;
      color: transparent;
      -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(240, 237, 230, 0.04);
      white-space: nowrap;
      pointer-events: none;
      user-select: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .waveform-wrap {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    #waveCanvas {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      opacity: 0.35;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow::before {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 40px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--rose);
    }

    .hero-h1 {
      font-size: clamp(72px, 10vw, 130px);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 38px);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      margin-bottom: 56px;
      max-width: 640px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .hero-sub em { color: var(--rose); font-style: normal; }

    .hero-cta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      max-width: 480px;
    }
    .hero-input {
      flex: 1;
      background: rgba(240, 237, 230, 0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
      border-right: none;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--off-white);
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .hero-input::placeholder { color: var(--warm-mid); }
    .hero-input:focus { border-color: var(--rose); }
    .btn-rose {
      background: var(--rose);
      color: var(--black);
      border: 1px solid var(--rose);
      padding: 16px 28px;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .btn-rose:hover { background: transparent; color: var(--rose); }

    .hero-scroll {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 40px;
      right: 48px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .hero-scroll::after {
      content: '';
      width: 1px;
      height: 60px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--rose), transparent);
      animation: drip 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes drip {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scaleY(1); }
      50% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleY(1.1); }
    }

    /* ─── STATS TICKER ─── */
    .stats-bar {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 20px 48px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .stat {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 0 40px 0 0;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--off-white);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat-num span { color: var(--rose); }
    .stat-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--warm-mid); letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; }

    /* ─── SECTION SHARED ─── */
    section { padding: 120px 48px; }
    .section-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      color: var(--rose);
    }
    .section-tag::before {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 24px;
      height: 1px;
      background: currentColor;
    }

    /* ─── VISION ─── */
    #vision {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 80px;
    }
    .vision-left {}
    .vision-h2 {
      font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .vision-body {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(240, 237, 230, 0.6);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .vision-right {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .signal-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 28px 32px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .signal-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-warm); }
    .signal-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
      width: 2px;
      background: var(--rose);
      transform: scaleY(0);
      transform-origin: bottom;
      transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    .signal-card:hover::before { transform: scaleY(1); }
    .signal-card-label { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .signal-card-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--off-white);
    }
    .signal-card-desc {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ─── HOW IT WORKS ─── */
    #tech {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .tech-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }
    .tech-h2 { font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 72px); max-width: 500px; }
    .tech-aside {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      max-width: 320px;
      text-align: right;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .step {
      padding: 40px 36px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      position: relative;
      background: var(--warm-faint);
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .step:hover { background: rgba(212, 115, 90, 0.04); }
    .step-num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 80px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(240, 237, 230, 0.06);
      position: absolute;
      top: 16px;
      right: 24px;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .step-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border: 1px solid var(--rose);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .step-icon svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; stroke: var(--rose); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.5; }
    .step-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .step-body {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ─── PRIVACY ─── */
    #privacy {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 80px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .privacy-h2 { font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 68px); margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .privacy-body {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .privacy-badges {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .badge {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .badge:hover { border-color: var(--rose); color: var(--rose); }

    .privacy-visual {
      position: relative;
      height: 400px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .lock-ring {
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      animation: spin-slow 20s linear infinite;
    }
    .lock-ring::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: -20px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 115, 90, 0.15);
      animation: spin-slow 12s linear infinite reverse;
    }
    .lock-ring::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: -40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(212, 115, 90, 0.07);
    }
    .lock-inner {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    .lock-inner strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--off-white);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    @keyframes spin-slow { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    .privacy-orbit {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
    }
    .orbit-label {
      position: absolute;
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(240, 237, 230, 0.25);
    }

    /* ─── FINAL CTA ─── */
    .final-cta {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 160px 48px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .final-cta-glow {
      position: absolute;
      width: 600px;
      height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212, 115, 90, 0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .final-cta h2 {
      font-size: clamp(52px, 8vw, 110px);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .final-cta p {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      margin-bottom: 56px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .final-cta-form {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      max-width: 440px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 40px 48px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    footer p {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .footer-links a {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--warm-mid);
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--rose); }

    /* ─── FADE IN ─── */
    .fade-up {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    .fade-up.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      header { padding: 24px; }
      nav { display: none; }
      .hero { padding: 0 24px 64px; }
      .hero-cta { max-width: 100%; }
      section { padding: 80px 24px; }
      #vision { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
      .tech-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 24px; }
      .tech-aside { text-align: left; }
      .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      #privacy { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .privacy-visual { height: 280px; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .stats-bar { flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; padding: 32px 24px; }
      .stat { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 24px; }
      .stat:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
      .final-cta { padding: 100px 24px; }
      .final-cta-form { max-width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header id="site-header">
    <a href="/" class="logo">EDG<span>E</span></a>
    <nav>
      <a href="#vision">Vision</a>
      <a href="#tech">Signal</a>
      <a href="#privacy">Privacy</a>
    </nav>
    <a href="#" class="btn-outline">Investor Deck</a>
  </header>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg-text">EDGE</div>

    <div class="waveform-wrap">
      <canvas id="waveCanvas"></canvas>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">
        <span class="mono-label">Pilot Access — 2026</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="display hero-h1">
        The Emotion<br />
        <em class="display-italic" style="color: var(--rose);">Operating</em><br />
        System.
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-sub">
        Bridging the millennia-old <em>Pleasure Gap</em> —<br />
        physiological signal decoded into synchronized guidance.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-cta">
        <input class="hero-input" type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" />
        <button class="btn-rose" onclick="handleWaitlist()">Join Pilot</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-scroll">
      <span class="mono-label" style="writing-mode: vertical-rl; letter-spacing: 0.3em;">Scroll</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS BAR -->
  <div class="stats-bar fade-up">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">57<span>%</span></span>
      <span class="stat-label">reported pleasure gap in heterosexual partnerships</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">∞</span>
      <span class="stat-label">guesswork replaced by real signal</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">0</span>
      <span class="stat-label">raw biometric data leaves your device</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num" style="font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Real<span style="color:var(--rose);">-</span>Time</span>
      <span class="stat-label">feedback, no post-session debrief</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VISION -->
  <section id="vision">
    <div class="vision-left fade-up">
      <div class="section-tag mono-label">The Problem</div>
      <h2 class="display vision-h2">
        Modern intimacy<br />
        <em class="display-italic">runs on guesswork.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="vision-body">
        Heart Rate Variability. Galvanic Skin Response.
        Two signals that contain the whole story — and until now,
        nobody was listening to them together, in real time.
      </p>
      <p class="vision-body">
        EDGE transforms consumer wearables into an intelligent
        interface. Not a survey. Not a score. A living conversation
        between bodies, mediated by data.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="vision-right fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.15s;">
      <div class="signal-card">
        <div class="mono-label signal-card-label">Signal 01 — HRV</div>
        <div class="signal-card-title">Heart Rate Variability</div>
        <div class="signal-card-desc">The millisecond oscillation between beats. A window into arousal, anxiety, and emotional presence that the conscious mind cannot fabricate.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="signal-card">
        <div class="mono-label signal-card-label">Signal 02 — GSR</div>
        <div class="signal-card-title">Galvanic Skin Response</div>
        <div class="signal-card-desc">Micro-sweat. Sympathetic nervous system activity rendered in microvoltage. The body speaking before the mouth can form words.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="signal-card">
        <div class="mono-label signal-card-label">Signal 03 — Sync</div>
        <div class="signal-card-title">Physiological Synchrony</div>
        <div class="signal-card-desc">When two people's autonomic rhythms begin to mirror each other. The quantifiable substrate of what we've always called chemistry.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="tech">
    <div class="tech-header fade-up">
      <h2 class="display tech-h2">
        Three signals.<br />
        One <em class="display-italic">score.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="tech-aside">
        "Time in Zone" — the duration partners sustain peak mutual
        pleasure states, quantified and acted on in real time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step fade-up">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="step-title">Capture</div>
        <div class="step-body">Pair any HRV-capable wearable. EDGE reads from the device API — no proprietary hardware required. Works day one.</div>
